00229%3Fs%3D19&h=a1c5f47d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kingkongcrew/status/1170322218565300229?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n再推！<br />\nretweets仲係太少。「核彈文宣」高質片解釋畀外國人聽點解要杯葛花木蘭同支持香港人權及民主法案"},{"pid":"5b0eb27459c4ac71f86d806cc237dd3e1f12d210","tid":1555973,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"勇武走得太前，後勤補給不足，文宣唔夠人！<br />\n做人要有公關！文宣多一個就好多！連儂牆要人！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衛城長久戰，生活中抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；<br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全之下，免費港鐵；二人同遊，一人免費<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！連繫左鄰右里<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2BumLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=b1a499f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 低消費，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF都買美股<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會事務，做陪審員啦<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.09"},{"pid":"f11a6363ab8cf5c56c88ebecb60b01202029749c","tid":1555973,"uid":93932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:58:26.000Z","msg":"今日既都已經有"},{"pid":"0782516fcc266225af03549d73a38fc26af07bc9","tid":1555973,"uid":8745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:58:48.000Z","msg":"又眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" c